<subSubSection lastPageId="3" lastPageNumber="370" pageId="1" pageNumber="368" type="description">
<paragraph lastPageId="3" lastPageNumber="370" pageId="1" pageNumber="368">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[214,340,540,563]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="368">Description</emphasis>
.Male. Length 
<quantity box="[491,647,540,563]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.95" metricValueMax="2.05" metricValueMin="1.85" pageId="1" pageNumber="368" unit="mm" value="1.95" valueMax="2.05" valueMin="1.85">1.85–2.05 mm</quantity>
, width 
<quantity box="[721,878,540,563]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.365" metricValueMax="1.46" metricValueMin="1.27" pageId="1" pageNumber="368" unit="mm" value="1.365" valueMax="1.46" valueMin="1.27">1.27–1.46 mm</quantity>
. Head, mouthparts, antennae, pronotum, hypomera, and tarsi ochreous. Anterior two thirds of elytra dark brown to blackish, apical third of elytra yellowish. Mesoventrite and metaventrite with epimera and anepisterna reddish-brown. Coxae, femora, tibiae and abdomen light brown, slightly lighter than metaventrite. Antennae with relative length/width of antennomeres as: 
<date box="[522,608,686,710]" pageId="1" pageNumber="368" value="2013-03-08">
III 
<number box="[557,585,686,710]" pageId="1" pageNumber="368" value="13.0">13</number>
/ 
<number box="[594,608,686,710]" pageId="1" pageNumber="368" value="8.0">8</number>
</date>
: 
<date box="[620,708,686,710]" pageId="1" pageNumber="368" value="1950-04-09">
IV 
<number box="[657,686,686,710]" pageId="1" pageNumber="368" value="50.0">50</number>
/ 
<number box="[695,708,686,710]" pageId="1" pageNumber="368" value="9.0">9</number>
</date>
: 
<date box="[720,792,686,710]" pageId="1" pageNumber="368" value="1973-05-09">
V 
<number box="[742,770,686,710]" pageId="1" pageNumber="368" value="73.0">73</number>
/ 
<number box="[779,792,686,710]" pageId="1" pageNumber="368" value="9.0">9</number>
</date>
: 
<date box="[804,905,686,710]" pageId="1" pageNumber="368" value="1960-06-10">
VI 
<number box="[841,870,686,710]" pageId="1" pageNumber="368" value="60.0">60</number>
/ 
<number box="[879,905,686,710]" pageId="1" pageNumber="368" value="10.0">10</number>
</date>
: 
<date box="[917,1027,686,710]" pageId="1" pageNumber="368" value="1965-07-12">
VII 
<number box="[963,991,686,710]" pageId="1" pageNumber="368" value="65.0">65</number>
/ 
<number box="[1000,1027,686,710]" pageId="1" pageNumber="368" value="12.0">12</number>
</date>
: 
<date box="[153,258,715,739]" pageId="1" pageNumber="368" value="1956-08-09">
